           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      09                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      72                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
