      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-buf-cli-iom-drc    to   v-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
