      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-buf-cli-iom-bco
                    (w-buf-cli-iom-c01)   to   w-buf-cli-iom-cod      .
           move      w-buf-cli-iom-bdp
                    (w-buf-cli-iom-c01)   to   w-buf-cli-iom-dpz      .
