      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     buf-cli-iom-999.
       buf-cli-iom-584.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Up                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-buf-cli-iom-c01      .
           if        w-buf-cli-iom-nli    =    07
                     go to buf-cli-iom-590
           else      go to buf-cli-iom-550.
       buf-cli-iom-586.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
