      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-buf-cli-iom-c01    <    w-buf-cli-iom-crb
                     add   1              to   w-buf-cli-iom-c01
                     go to buf-cli-iom-588
           else      go to buf-cli-iom-575.
       buf-cli-iom-588.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
