           divide    6                    into w-buf-cli-iom-c02      .
           move      w-buf-cli-iom-c02    to   w-buf-cli-iom-cpa      .
           subtract  1                    from w-buf-cli-iom-c02      .
           multiply  6                    by   w-buf-cli-iom-c02      .
           add       1                    to   w-buf-cli-iom-c02      .
